Earlier, my project was SQL-focused where I manually executed scripts and procedures in SSMS. Later, I enhanced it into an end-to-end automated ETL pipeline using Python. Now Python extracts CSV data, loads Bronze tables, executes Silver stored procedures, validates Gold tables, generates Excel dashboards, logs execution details, handles errors, and can be scheduled using Windows Task Scheduler.
